HEADWORD: Inductance
<hw>In*duc"tance</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <fld>(Elec.)</fld>
<def>Capacity for induction; the coefficient of
self-induction.</def></p>

<p><note>⟦hand⟧ The unit of inductance is the
<unit>henry</unit>.</note>⟦br⟧
[<source>Webster 1913 Suppl.</source>]</p>

